<div id="u-credit-00426-hovertip">
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/yyue" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5044404); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5044404&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610180085" alt="yyue" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5044404)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/yyue" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5044404); return false;">yyue</a></span></p>
